{"tid":1894864,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"驚！南韓39人朝聖團訪以色列　回國後28人確診武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-02-24T07:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T03:38:10.000Z","uid":35519,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"2b4f92270e078c1054e2145e2b3449cd68250a26","tid":1894864,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:58:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>驚！<br />\n南韓39人朝聖團訪以色列　<br />\n回國後28人確診武漢肺炎</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/02/24/phpxAPvX0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F02%2F24%2FphpxAPvX0.jpg&h=9c337018&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國武漢爆發的新型冠狀病毒引發的肺炎（COVID-19，下稱武漢肺炎）疫情擴散，<ins>南韓一團39人赴以色列的朝聖團，被診斷有多人感染，返韓後有18人陸續確診，今當局宣布該朝聖團再增10人確診，<strong>全團39人有28人遭感染</strong>。</ins><br />\n<br />\n據《韓聯社》報導，南韓一團共39人的朝聖團在8日至16日期間在以色列巡禮朝聖，不料返韓後有18人分別在21、22日確診，今南韓慶尚北道政府再宣布，這團又新增10例確診病例，累計已達28人受感染；<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">當局表示，其中大部分確診患者回國第二天就去溫泉、餐廳等公共設施或正常上班，甚至參加了團體活動，恐爆發社區傳播。</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>研判可能在韓國感染新冠病毒後 旅遊期間發生交叉感染</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n南韓中央防疫對策本部指出，鑑於這些人員是慶北地區居民，加上以色列當地尚未出現社區傳播的情況，他們很可能在國內感染新冠病毒後在旅遊期間發生交叉感染，具體感染途經正在調查當中；目前南韓境內武漢肺炎確診數達763人、7例不治。<br />\n<br />\n另外又有一團28人的以色列旅行團將於今下午返回南韓，慶尚北道和安東市政府計劃讓這些人員乘坐地方政府安排的專車前往臨時安置點接受隔離；由於南韓旅遊團恐攜病毒入境，以色列22日下午宣布禁止日本及南韓班機入境，1架南韓客機隨後降落於以色列特拉維夫機場，但機上除以色列公民外約有200人都遭原機遣返。"},{"pid":"dbf41f837d2882ef20b01fb8df89667a80f45e4d","tid":1894864,"uid":35519,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:00:22.000Z","msg":"唔怪之得呢兩日原機遣返啲韓國人返去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac4e0efc980839d71a6865843f79ee1851dd679","tid":1894864,"uid":52946,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:01:26.000Z","msg":"以色列多得你唔少呀泡菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b7f9b5a3c8ce573b57dcffa885529936767356","tid":1894864,"uid":39365,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:03:00.000Z","msg":"巴勒斯坦等緊以色列滅國不是夢"},{"pid":"cb918ae0137ca82a875c42b62f9ce7b99ec885e9","tid":1894864,"uid":11454,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1313/0*UhPlUPD140Z5Gh9K.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1313%2F0%2AUhPlUPD140Z5Gh9K.gif&h=859b9e78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed95d35b9b87a106c5785d5a00d4df764414e55d","tid":1894864,"uid":293557,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:03:59.000Z","msg":"天國的<del>階梯</del><br />\n<del>愛的</del>逼降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50edcc193689da22fcb5eba60a386f9ac469fb5a","tid":1894864,"uid":331421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:06:32.000Z","msg":"猶太人太審判2.0"},{"pid":"51141bbeab902af2b907d038f1fe7cb02fc90e35","tid":1894864,"uid":76854,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cb918ae0137ca82a875c42b62f9ce7b99ec885e9","tid":1894864,"uid":11454,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1313/0*UhPlUPD140Z5Gh9K.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1313%2F0%2AUhPlUPD140Z5Gh9K.gif&h=859b9e78&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:07:54.000Z","msg":"第十人理論都失效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c76cc045ea6b77f090615699c93942c7186bbc","tid":1894864,"uid":33370,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:20:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZJvEB2F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx